Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,弥娅哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们一起变湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1086,981)\fs57}宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.52,Comment,,0,0,0,,注：日语里宣誓音同变湿，这里是双关。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一起宣言我们永远不会长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:46.84,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,<list:item>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:47.84,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,\h\h<i:这个肉体>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.00,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,\h\h<i:这个乳房>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.55,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,\h\h<i:这个那里>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.63,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,\h\h<i:这个子宫>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.13,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,</list>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是我自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如此向世界肃然敬告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,自出生之时体内就被嵌入WatchMe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不仅没有疑惑反而感激不已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们长大成人  WatchMe就会自己启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,连长胖  死亡的自由都被它夺去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这个乳房的成长也被生府所掌握所管理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs57\fnArial\fsp-1.5\pos(1054,981)}Vigorment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,图安你能对这种事忍气吞声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,松手啊  弥娅哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的身体被WatchMe用文字和数字所替换
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事能容忍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是绝不能接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,弥娅哈…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
