Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.10,0:38:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我没有回到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我没有和姬安再会
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,或许她就不会死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.18,0:38:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,弥娅哈曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.98,0:38:17.48,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,<maxim>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.48,0:38:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要人有心
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.54,0:38:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夺去人的生命这种事是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.36,0:38:22.86,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,</maxim>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.00,0:38:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.48,0:38:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们体内还藏有能够破坏更加重要的东西的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.80,0:38:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,15岁的弥娅哈如是说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.80,0:38:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姬安  是这个论断迟了13年的证明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.33,0:38:38.33,ETML:ARID,,0,0,0,,{\an7}<movie:ar:id=8dhkie470267k9448s>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.22,0:38:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而我  又一次被抛下了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.56,0:38:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,5天
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.42,0:38:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我所得到的解明姬安之死的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.51,0:38:53.66,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,<fear>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.66,0:38:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我过去大概没有理解姬安
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.94,0:38:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,姬安是这么坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.54,0:39:15.04,ETML:Default,,0,0,0,,<horror>
